==Absolute convergence over sets==

A generalization of the absolute convergence of a series, is the absolute convergence of a sum of a function over a set. We can first consider a countable set formula_39 and a function formula_123 We will give a definition below of the sum of formula_124 over formula_46 written as formula_126 

